{"title":"腊月，梧桐的悬铃","authors":["刘毅"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":1,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月，梧桐的悬铃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾误认是阿谀作颂的编钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾斥之为桀纣王冠的流苏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是当肃杀到生机全无"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连空气都寒颤得几乎冻僵时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"性格才在燃烧中明亮起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风中摇曳的舞步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踢踏着冬的秩序"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那如鸣珮环的清音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那嘲笑淫威的乐观活泼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题写着一首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战退严冬的绿色的诗"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}